    "The results show that fundus image AI for DR screening primarily relies on deep learning (DL) algorithms.",
    "Currently, external validation of DL models for DR diagnostics is underway in regions with a high volume of publications.",
    "Additionally, several AI-based DR screening platforms have received approval and are being marketed by national regulatory authorities in the United States, Europe, Singapore, and China.",
    "The results demonstrate a clear correlation between the number of articles published in the field of AI-based DR screening and the advancement of AI technology.",
    "This is illustrated in Figure 1, which depicts the growth of articles in this field over time."
